items.name: Saitou / Bea (Pokemon)
items.description:
Lora model of Saitou (Bea) from Pokemon series. Preview images mostly done with weight 1 (had to lower slightly with some other loras).

Submitting this faster than expected because my vacation was cut short by a literal hellfire (volcano eruption). This is actually version 15 of the model xD because before leaving I used it for experiments and tried doing it in few different ways. Not many serious attempts among those, but it did helped make final version better :)

Example prompts:

  • Regular outfit - bea \(pokemon\), bow hairband, print shirt, tied shirt, black bodysuit, bodysuit under clothes, single glove, print shorts, knee pads, barefoot

  • Just bodysuit - bea \(pokemon\), bow hairband, black bodysuit, single glove, knee pads, barefoot - if you're getting bodysuit with collar, best remedy is to add collarbone to prompt. This also somewhat prevents fist logo from appearing.

  • School uniform - bea \(pokemon\), bow hairband, school uniform, white shirt, black skirt, sneakers

  • Palentine outfit - bea (pokemon), alternate costume, black hairband, hair ornament, red scarf, white sweater, brown dress, black pantyhose - even better if you add bow hairband into negatives. Also if you're getting just hairband without flower on it, you can put more weight on hair ornament or even just add flower.

items.name: Stomachs, Tentacles, etc. Background
items.description:
A LoRA to generate stomach internals, fleshy tentacle pits, and occasionally other orifices left to your imagination.

Requires the LyCORIS extension.

Triggers

Primary trigger: tentacle cave background

Strongly recommended trigger: liquid acid puddle

Additional optional triggers: wet, dripping, steam

Recommended Models

Not designed for realistic models.

SXZ Luma works quite well.

Trained on, and very compatible with AnyLoRA.

Tips

Carefully select quality-related positives like (best quality, masterpiece) or (best quality, masterpiece, realistic) and negatives like (low quality, worst quality:1.4), (art by bad-artist-anime:0.9). Don't go overboard with them however, as they may destroy the effect.

EasyNegative and likely other negative embeddings can make things look more biologically disgusting. Maybe what you're after, maybe not.

Multiple tags describing what you want in the stomach helps it appear. For example, 1girl may not always work. 1girl, blonde hair or 1girl, surprised is more likely.

This model is trained as a background, and takes advantage of the base model's pre-existing understanding of a tentacle cave to shift things into a fleshy stomachy kind of look. Some models "get" the concept and some don't. If stuff is coming out fried, try lowering the LoRA weight, playing with the CFG scale, or trying a different model.

--

DISCLAIMER:

I'm doing this for fun and not for commercial motive, My main purpose is to compose a fictional character using AI with the beauty of all persons above, please support them if you love their works. i do not support any indecent images generated of all persons in this model, I do not support selling generated images of persons in this model. please refrain to what they have been posting online.

All persons in this models are 21+ and not a minor, please DO NOT post explicit nudity, suggestive content, or pornographic content online using this model. Refer to CivitAi TOS for more details.

===

Request or Suggestion Rule:

  1. No request of minor!

  2. The requested should have public data (no private)

  3. Should have more than 30 good quality images

  4. Since all requests or suggestion are free, I will still need to like your request, otherwise its a work not a hobby for me.

  5. Be a decent human being and leave a review if your requests is up It takes you only 5 mins while it takes me hours, electricity, and efforts to do your requests.

  6. If you don't get what you want, do not review bomb, there could be other creators models or lora that can get better results than mine, use theirs instead, and leave a good review on them too, support any other creators for their hardworks!

NOTE : I will keep updating more actresses in versions update

===

Usage Guide

--

A. Lora Weight

  • 0.1 ~ 0.4 -- is to combine multiple faces or features, or if you experience overbaking

  • 0.5 ~ 0.7 -- is a balanced weight to get still accurate feature but with more flexiblity

  • 0.8 ~ 1.0 -- is to create accurate representation of the features.

B. CFG Scale

  • Lower CFG Scale means AI gets more creative and less overbaking problems.

  • Higher CFG Scale means results get very accurate with training sets and more prone to overbaking problems.

  • Dynamic CFG Threshold, using this method allows you to bump up quality and achieve photorealistic easily, but with lycoris i found out recently that this method actually lower success rate, so only use when you are composing with a Lora / model that works fine with this method.

C. Sampling Steps, High Res Fix & Upscaling

  • I like to use sampling steps at 50, with high res step at 20, or 1/2 of sampling steps.

  • I find that 2M Karras works better and faster than SDE Karras. with ERSGAN 4x+ method + ERSGAN 4x for Upscaling. This method actually gives quite good result without being too sharp or too plasticky

  • Upscaling - GPFGAN @0.25, Codeformer @0.3 & Codeformer Weight @0.15 seems to yield superior results to me.

--

Combining with Attribute LoRa / LyCoris

You may need to do your own testing, but using character at weight -0.2 below attribute lora weight yields superior results, if for some reason one features persists not showing or overbake, you may want to lower the weight of the overbaked feature Lora, and then use emphasis () to boost the specific attribute you want.

DDetailer / ADetailer Script

If subject face is small / far away use: DDetailer Script with bbox anime face with default settings except denoiser at 0.2-0.3. You can combine this LoRa with a lot of other Style / Attire / Pose / Acts LoRa, Also works well with character LyCoris.

How to install this script? I kinda forget how because its a bit complicated beacuse you need to install stuff from venv. but a quick google search will land you somewhere in tutorial page.

Enjoy.

This LoRA was created specifically for use with WarpFusion and img2img.

It will reliably produce scenery and landscapes similar to what you see in the showcase photos here.

It will work for text2img, but the suggested prompt/token weights you'll see here might not directly apply or result in quality images.

'(cpc:1.4), flat color, (masterpiece, extremely detailed, 4k, 8k, 16k, highres:1.3), <lora:cpc_warp:0.95>'

The negative prompt was constructed using the "Fast Negative Embedding" available here: https://civitai.com/models/71961/fast-negative-embedding

Suggested Negative Prompt for WarpFusion:

'FastNegativeEmbedding, (out of frame, out of focus), (monochrome)'

items.name: Kay - Hentai University
items.description:
This is a LoRA for the character Kay, from Hentai University a game by Noodle Jacuzzi.

Kay's art is from the artist Akagai, the set -

Tenshi Mitaina Hentai Inran Sister to IchaLove Sex!

I've been working my way through making these for all the characters currently in the game, and sharing them in the Discord for HU, but figured I should also put them up here.

In general, I'm working from pretty limited image sets, so expect the results to be a bit wonky at times. Add in this being one of the otoko no ko/femboy characters, and how much the AI struggles with that occasionally... It turned out as well as it could have, but you know how the AI is with penises.

I recommend a weight of around 0.5, possibly lower depending if you're combining the character LoRA with other styles/costumes/etc. along with tagging some defining characteristics of the character you're generating. Higher than that can really push the artist's original style, and may cause you issues.

All characters I train have a "character tag" added into the set to help generate them fairly reliably.

Recommended LoRA Weight - 0.5 for fairly flexible, higher if you want more of the original artist's style, lower if it doesn't play nice with other loras.

Character tag - HUKay, 1boy, flat chest
Recommended tags - blonde hair, sidelocks, blue eyes,

I suppose you could always tag 1girl and give the guy some breasts, but if you want the original experience, be sure to tag for it.

I've got quite a backlog of these made up already, so I'll be uploading them on and off.

Check my other uploads as I put them out for more HU characters, and if you want any specific character put up soon, let me know.

items.description:
The cute villainess and bully bait Heine from the anime/manga series.

How to use
Use the tags "1girl" and "h3ine" and then prompt away. Naturally, drop the "1girl" if you want to add more characters to the image. If your model needs more tags try "ahoge" and "white hair". For more things to try please see the uploaded zip with training tags.

Her default outfit is tagged as "thigh boots", "waist cape", "detached sleeves", "revealing clothes", "red sleeves", "highleg", "brooch", "choker" though generally only "revealing clothes" should be enough.
Since Heine only wears the same outfit with a short exception it can bleed over, the above tags can also be used in negatives to block it.
As for her red dress it's tagged as "halter dress" though how well that works depends a lot on your model since it's not a very strong tag in most.

Don't forget to review and upload your own images, it's always fun to see what you're creating!
Like my LoRAs and want more? Please consider a small tip towards my electricity bill and further training >.<

Trained on NAI with 32 pretty rough screencaps extended with three generated images from a previous LoRA version.

Game World is a project by TheFoodMage.

Art from the model from Food Mage has been gathered over the last 3 years, so there are over 500 images in the training data, of digital art from a real 3D artist. Please wait on the cool updates

Please follow the permissions to users - do not use this to make money or for your own merges. My art style is pretty recognizable. A lot of artists hate AI or are scared of it for this reason. I am not.

Generate using a weight of 0.4-1 like this: <lora:crabPeoplev120:0.7>


How I archived my generations:

  1. txt2img: DPM++ SDE Karras with 20 steps,512x512(can go up to 768 for wide or tall), Restore faces on (using CodeFormer weight 1.0 in Settings), Hires-fix on, to 1024x1024 (double original size) with your preferred upscaler and Denoise 0.5, CFG 7. Then send to img2img!

  2. img2img: DPM++ SED Karras with 20 steps, Restore faces on (CodeFormer weight 1), rescale to 1536x1536, CFG 7, Denoise between 0.3-0.7 (based on how much you want to improve the image), SAME PROMPT! Send to extras when happy with img2img/inpaint results.

  3. extras: Scale to x3 (final will be 4608x4608, I suggest going lower, I did x3 just for the samples here) Upscaler 1 - FatalAnime 4x, Upscaler 2 - SwinIR 4x with 0.10 visibility, GFPGAN 0.10 visibility, CodeFormer 0.10 visibility.

items.name: [Umi AI] Aphrodite v2
items.description:
To avoid confusion: UMI AI is not necesarry to get these gens, all of these were done without using it.

Umi AI is a premier replacement mod for Wildcards that many people have been using since they first appeared in October 2022. Umi AI is not only an incredible extension for rapidly generating randomized prompts of all sorts of people, creatures, and settings, but it is now also an Embedding Repository with organized and credited embeds from across the internet. Join the Umi Discord today!

This model release for Umi AI is for the realism model series dubbed Aphrodite.

Aphrodite v2: A model capable of generating realistic people, landscapes and paintings. It should be able to do both SFW and NSFW alike, and it is extremely flexible in how you can prompt it!
(Version 1 can be found here: https://civitai.com/models/6077/umi-ai-mythology-and-babes-by-dutchalex)

What makes these models so special? Well, I'm glad you asked. No longer do you need to add Masterpiece, High Quality, or other such things to your prompts. Now, you can much more easily change the style of an output. UmiAI comes with wildcards tested on and designed for all these models, and notably they work really well with the different artstyles Umi can produce. Even Aphrodite can often generate anime-styling well!

For more info, check out the Umi AI page where you can find install instructions here:

https://www.patreon.com/posts/umi-ai-official-73544634

If you want to learn how to better improve your promptcrafting, join the Umi AI Discord today! This also helps Umi AI become the best possible system for generating prompts and making characters come to life! We'd also love to see what you come up with as well!

items.name: Chyler Leigh
items.description:
A commission of @Zorglub.

Chyler Leigh is an American actress, singer and model, mainly known for her roles in TV shows such as Grey's Anatomy and Supergirl.

1020-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images with my¬†usual settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of beautiful (chyleigh:0.99), a woman as a movie star, hair upsweep updo, sweater off-shoulders, trousers, at a movie premiere gala, dark moody ambience (masterpiece:1.2) (photorealistic:1.2) (bokeh) (best quality) (detailed skin:1.2) (intricate details) (nighttime) (8k) (HDR) (cinematic lighting) (sharp focus), (looking at the camera:1.1), (closeup portrait:1.1)"
